 ruler can be persuaded through patience,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and a gentle tongue can break a bone. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 15:1","book":"Pro","chapter":15,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 16:14","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 16:32","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":32,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ec 10:4","book":"Ecc","chapter":10,"verse":4,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 15:1","book":"Pro","chapter":15,"verse":1},{"label":"Pr 16:14","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":14},{"label":"Pr 16:32","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":32},{"label":"Ec 10:4","book":"Ecc","chapter":10,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:25:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If you find honey, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 14:8","book":"Jdg","chapter":14,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 14:25","book":"1Sa","chapter":14,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" eat only what you need;"},{"kind":"text","text":" otherwise, you’ll get sick from it and vomit. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 25:27","book":"Pro","chapter":25,"verse":27,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jdg 14:8","book":"Jdg","chapter":14,"verse":8},{"label":"1Sm 14:25","book":"1Sa","chapter":14,"verse":25},{"label":"Pr 25:27","book":"Pro","chapter":25,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:25:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Seldom set foot in your neighbor’s house;"},{"kind":"text","text":" otherwise, he’ll get sick of you and hate you."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Pro:25:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"A person giving false testimony against his neighbor "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 20:16","book":"Exo","chapter":20,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 24:28","book":"Pro","chapter":24,"verse":28,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" is like a club, a sword, or a s